Taylor Graves https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Taylor_Graves 0 Taylor Graves (28 May 1896 – October 30, 1960), was an American stage, screen and radio actor. He appeared in 9 films between 1921 and 1926. He enjoyed a long stage career.He was born in Alameda, California, United States and died in New York City.
